 l knowthey don't say to you,
 go thieving,

665
01:45:32,120 --> 01:45:35,120
 but they let you know:
 steal but don't get greedy.

666
01:45:35,720 --> 01:45:38,720
 Take what you need
 and don't meddle.

667
01:45:40,120 --> 01:45:43,120
 Am l right?

668
01:45:48,880 --> 01:45:51,880
