 l'm a policeman myself.

678
01:47:25,440 --> 01:47:27,879
 Then why the fucking around?

679
01:47:27,880 --> 01:47:30,399
 lf you're asked for documents,
 give them.

680
01:47:30,400 --> 01:47:33,400
